name: Untitled #13
description:
A smaller version of my bigger photo work.
In this series, I use small colorful treasures found or saved from parental home.

This work is 18 x 18 cm (7.1 "x 7.1") with an edge.
So that you can put it in frame or paspartout.
The work is printed on Epson Premium Semi Gloss 251gr and printed with Epson Archival pigment inks for lifelong durability,brilliant colors and with a silky shine coating.

Open edition.

Each print is signed and dated on the back. And is carefully packaged for shipment.
So it is in good condition at your home ..

* Colors may vary slightly from screen to screen.
* Printed without my name.

** More pictures at www.eyesnacks.nl **
